Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:27.20,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.19,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.61,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:41.48,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:49.22,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:55.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:23:00.06,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:06.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:14.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.81,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:36.28,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:45.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえるその声が 私の涙強くする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:49.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:27.20,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是劃過我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.19,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想開始悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.61,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們觸碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:41.48,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:49.22,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過玻璃星星看到你的側臉 讓人如此無法割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:55.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 卻也無法向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:23:00.06,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出種種借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避著現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:06.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我如此膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:14.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於鼓起勇氣直面那潰不成軍的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧 打開通向明天的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.81,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你傾訴那份一直未說出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:36.28,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這坦誠相對的世界裡 向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:45.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的聲音 讓我的眼淚也變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:49.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是劃過我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們坐同桌還是頭一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離諏訪君也很近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟他離得有點兒遠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君 會不會喜歡吃捲心菜肉卷呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 有意味深長的電波正在飛來飛去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒飛來飛去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 認真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相會是怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 別生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是透過玻璃窗也無所謂的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}這個……是術語麼？透過玻璃窗也可以接吻的人麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是完全不認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全……不認識什麼的……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是不好的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 真是死板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛上任的班長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好嗎 還隔著玻璃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特納西·塔科特君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是渡邊加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興能坐在你附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是透過玻璃窗也無所謂的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 可能不是吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是要先申明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說結婚……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……是那個「結婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 人妻高中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請叫我Mrs渡邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後 有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 稍微陪我一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是love love呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新籐諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是也是透過玻璃窗也無所謂的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車輪啊 車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我彷彿正在被本該由我駕馭的巨大的車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碾碎……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是三年級的遠籐紗理奈部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是特納西·塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨戲劇部「夜間飛行」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位你已經認識了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的山姿夏加學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及與我們同一年級的姿芽泰加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別叫我「學姐」 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 在學校裡不要叫「少爺」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢啊 別這樣副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部長……是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的美少年氣場散發出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合登上舞台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你啟動了Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是標誌？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個是什麼留下的傷痕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}津津有味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕和標誌重疊在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒聽說過這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多想問的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 他昨晚是為了保護和子而戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白馬王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙綁架她的理由是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 你啟動Cybody的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的世界變成什麼樣了 你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入奇怪的空間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只有在那個奇怪的空間Cybody才能行動自如
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啟動cybody 世界的時間就會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在cybody只有在那個zero空間才能夠活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在普通的時空中不過是個巨大的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果能在普通的時空中活動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從軍事政治經濟各方面世界都會發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而以此為目的的傢伙現在正在這個島上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(619,224)}綺羅星十字團的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第二隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Banishing Age」代表人 首領
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第三隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Bougainvilleae」代表人 Everonu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第四隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成人銀行」代表人 頭取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第五隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Filament」代表人 Scarlet Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第六隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「科學工會」代表人 格林教授（Professor Green）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 綺羅星十字團總會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我們解開了氣多之巫女的封印進入了第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於用電氣柩使cybody活動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 各位 我們快樂日子也伴隨著新試煉的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實中坐上了cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是第三階段？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其那個沒見過的cybody道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀了我們夥伴的cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 「Filament」的擅自行動也是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開南方女巫的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算以後行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為有成員暴走表示抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝腔作勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應由「Filament」自身承擔責任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰該負責？雖然現在首領擁有指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不是支配著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不管怎樣領導總是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今晚的提案……怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說敵對的cybody是不可原諒的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個讓人不快的道伯恩擊破的人當然就是領導
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在踏上旅途之前都保有指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無異議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無異議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無異議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無異議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予我們榮光 然後帶給銀河美少年毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事和應該做的事合二為一的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能聽見世界的聲音麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 對人生的……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍長！現在是男生的入浴時間啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪裡進來的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一年級學生中很流行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔著玻璃接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有玻璃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔著不存在的玻璃接吻不就是個普通的吻嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又穿著泳衣做100回單槓翻轉上槓麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來看銀河美少年的屁股的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬治怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}上一集給出的資料為本田逢司 以後將會按照官網更名為本田喬治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alephisto被破壞了連StarDriver的資格都被剝奪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙意外的韌性很強所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能就這麼結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會去復仇吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的話一定能成功 但是急不來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓希望之星閃耀是我們「Filament」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長你不認為塔科特可能是他們的間諜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不認為哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你能斷言他不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和副部長關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在說認真的話題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很認真的在說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於那些傢伙開始直接瞄準和子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明擁有能夠操作最強Cybody並能使用Apprivoiser的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻不使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我在阻止著他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的和其他的人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被如此重視著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二位的婚約關係 他已經知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概從別人那裡聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好舒服的風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字學園嗎 太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yes yes yes yes 太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}蕩漾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet Kiss的第一個階段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是操縱親吻過的男人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那傢伙確實真的愛慕著新籐諏訪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人通常都不擅長等待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很快就會行動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魚 和我說說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長 薑汁汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在的心情到底是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我可能是為了和那些傢伙戰鬥才來到了這個島的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事請不要這麼隨便地說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該早就預料到在外面也有Star Driver了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是和那些傢伙沒有任何關係的有著正義感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這和今後將持續下去的戰鬥完全不是一碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是盡快轉學的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 若綺羅星的人馬教起真格來他是戰勝不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎 稍微點些什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年墜入了愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在海濱相遇的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年陷入了熱戀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 是愛情故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是屬於魚的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦 小魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年是一個手法很嫻熟的漁民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字的話Sam怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sam 很好的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年Sam夢見自己以及與他邂逅的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上小船 在光彩奪目的銀河世界裡暢遊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Sam愛上的是那個少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那銀河的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為人生的冒險仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟吧 電力柩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們都幹掉吧 Treteriauto！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著天體伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到轉瞬即逝的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的一切都在黑白畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}悄然凍結的白色吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}想要傳達的話語化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}肯定只有那份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 快點座上來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓我多等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}才能籠罩天空使它變得明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接嘴唇接觸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有隔玻璃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}被悲傷浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}向著重疊的純白色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把皆水之巫女的封印解開麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}我懷抱著無限溫柔的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}在無人知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}等待黎明的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}滿載光輝踏上旅途的我有著無可預測的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}飄舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}向著天體伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}深信著轉瞬即逝的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}一切的未來都在黑白畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯爽登場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太搶風頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍打出頭鳥 這句話你明白麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作真敏捷 是因為已經在第三階段了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把他毀掉有點可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可不是個外行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能容忍你們胡作非為了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓你們對島上的巫女們出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可不會像昨晚一樣了哦 銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我的氣勢可是高達1億伏特啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不討厭純真的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這一手 這可是個危機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 哲也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有我們filament 綺羅星才會如此閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧 塔科特君 已經夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算心懷恐懼 也要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服恐懼 勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的終極一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Τ射线的光芒啊！将银河充斥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Τ讀作Tau 為希臘字母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃爍吧 Τ銀河光線！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的出頭鳥啊 就算你打他他也會出頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的仇 我一定會替你報的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的肚子……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆麻煩來份捲心菜肉卷一份蛋包飯還有一份蛤肉羹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢是青春的特權！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有生活費確實是個危機啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一人獨居的女高中生的家裡？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 STAR DRIVER 閃亮的塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的銀河 一定閃爍著耀眼的光輝！
